<l>avaṟṟuḷ a i u</l>
<l>e o eṉṉu mappā laintu</l>
<l>mōraḷa picaikkuṅ kuṟṟeḻut teṉpa</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Among them,</l>
<l>the five sounds</l>
<l><foreign xml:lang="ta">a, i, u, e, o</foreign></l>
<l>have each one measure<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">aḷapu</foreign> ' measure, quantity '.</note></l>
<l>[and] are called short sounds.<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">kuṟṟeḻuttu.</foreign></note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
